    <workgroup>IMAP APPEND Extensions</workgroup>
    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document defines an extension to the IMAP service whereby a server can inform the client about maximum message upload sizes, allowing the client to avoid sending APPEND commands that will fail because the messages are too large.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
